The True Jesus Church is an independent Christian church that was established in Beijing, China in 1917. Today there are 1.5 million members in forty five countries. The church belongs to to the Protestant group of Christianity. Christmas and Easter are not celebrated.

The ten basic beliefs of the church are:

#Baptism
#Holy Communion
#Feet washing
#Holy Bible
#Salvation
#The Last Judgement
#Holy Spirit
#Sabbath day (Saturday)
#Jesus Christ

